<br>
By the time he came around I was doing the limit (and being passed by every other damn car on the highway /rude)... so anywho this cop tailgates me, so I flash him with my brakes... keeps tail-gating so I pull over THEN he flashes me (asshole).  Then the jerk struts over with his hand on his pistol and I'm like 'oh great'... so anyway, I naturally keep both hands on the wheel.  He was like &quot;you know you were speeding&quot; and I said &quot;I was staying with traffic to be safe&quot;... then he asks &quot;so where is your radar detector?&quot;... I almost laughed in his face, and I say &quot;I don't have one, but you can search my vehicle if you want&quot;... then he gets all excited when he sees my radio alarm clock in the back (I was relocating at the time) and I was like *oh god don't laugh in his face* and after I told him it was a clock he got a sad puppy dog look and slumped dejectedly back to his car hahaha<br>
